OL,3,CIce cream parlour scammed by fake #50
OL,4,Cnotes three times in same store
OL,6,FAn ice cream parlour in Cowbridge has
OL,7,Fbeen "stung" by a thief, who used
OL,8,Fthree fake #50 notes to buy ice cream.
OL,10,FFablas, which has recently opened a
OL,11,Fbranch in the town, say a man entered
OL,12,Ftheir store on three separate
OL,13,Foccasions on the same day to use the
OL,14,Fcounterfeit notes.
OL,16,FThe man is said to have fooled three
OL,17,Fdifferent members of staff at the shop
OL,18,Fby purchasing ice cream worth #3.50,
OL,19,Fmeaning he left with #46.50 change
OL,20,Feach time.
