OL,6,FAfter an internet search they
OL,7,Fdiscovered that fake notes can be
OL,8,Fidentified by scrunching them up with
OL,9,Fthe print falling off.
OL,11,FMs Evans says after finding out the
OL,12,Fnotes were indeed fake, she wants
OL,13,Fother businesses to be made aware of
OL,14,Fthe issue and be extra vigilant.
OL,16,F"We posted it on social media to make
OL,17,Fother business owners aware that this
OL,18,Fthreat is very real and to make sure
OL,19,Fthat people understand that these
OL,20,Fcounterfeit notes are out there.
