OL,6,F"We've taken them (the notes) across
OL,7,Fall our stores to show our staff this
OL,8,Fis what you need to look out for,
OL,9,Falthough they're passing the pen test
OL,10,Fgive them a scrunch, if the paint
OL,11,Fstarts coming off them then please
OL,12,Fdon't accept them."
OL,14,FMs Evans says the businesses is now
OL,15,Fhaving to find more money to pay for
OL,16,Fequipment that can detect if a note is
OL,17,Fcounterfeit or not.
