OL,6,F"We are going to have to invest in
OL,7,Fthese electric cash checkers and they
OL,8,Fplug in under a UV light. We will
OL,9,Finvest in one of those for each of our
OL,10,Fstores but they're around #60 each,
OL,11,Fthat's four stores, that's #240 so
OL,12,Fthat's a lot of money to fork out and
OL,13,Fwe're down #139.50 already before
OL,14,Fwe've even started.
OL,16,F"These counterfeits are just getting
OL,17,Fbetter and better and we just need to
OL,18,Fbe more vigilant as a business and
OL,19,Ftrain our staff adequately to ensure
OL,20,Fthey don't accept counterfeit note."
