OL,6,F"We work unbelievably hard for the
OL,7,Fmoney that we do earn and times are
OL,8,Ftough, people don't have that
OL,9,Fdisposable income anymore do they. So
OL,10,Fit's frustrating and really
OL,11,Fdisheartening but we've just got to
OL,12,Flearn from it now and move on."
OL,14,FMs Evans also says that she doesn't
OL,15,Fwant to deter customers from using
OL,16,Fcash.
