OL,6,F"We don't want to lose that clientele
OL,7,Fwho prefer to use cash because there
OL,8,Fare still people out there and it's so
OL,9,Ffrustrating when you go somewhere and
OL,10,Fthey only accept card, we know all too
OL,11,Fwell."
OL,13,FFablas has been running as a business
OL,14,Ffor seven years and Ms Evans says
OL,15,Fthey're lucky that this is the first
OL,16,Ftime they've been stung in this way
OL,17,Fwith counterfeit notes.
