OL,6,FReacting to the incident South Wales
OL,7,FPolice have said: "on 30 July, we were
OL,8,Fcontacted by a business in Cowbridge
OL,9,Fwhich reported being given three fake
OL,10,F#50 notes on July 22.
OL,12,F"This appears to be an isolated
OL,13,Freport, however local business are
OL,14,Fencouraged to be vigilant when
OL,15,Freceiving goods and services for cash
OL,16,Fand to report incidents to us.
OL,18,F"Enquiries into the incident in
OL,19,FCowbridge are underway."
